40分鐘,接著再用160度c繼續烘烤10-15分鐘。搖動模型時,蛋糕表面會像布丁般緩緩搖動的半熟狀態,即代表完成。請依各家烤箱的不同,烘烤時間可做調整。 烤箱先預熱170度c備用。烤模放入大烤盤裡,注入約2cm高度的熱水,放進烤箱以170度c烘烤40分鐘,接著再用160度c繼續烘烤10-15分鐘。搖動模型時,蛋糕表面會像布丁般緩緩搖動的半熟狀態,即代表完成。請依各家烤箱的不同,烘烤時間可做調整。 蛋糕出爐先冷卻後,再放入冰箱冷藏1個小時以上。用刀子沿著模型輕輕劃一圈,取下蛋糕即完成。 蛋糕出爐先冷卻後,再放入冰箱冷藏1個小時以上。用刀子沿著模型輕輕劃一圈,取下蛋糕即完成。"},{"pid":"a770a628d9fc4bd39cf4e5f81f64c177c84cccb9","tid":517154,"uid":46769,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T04:54:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://data.whicdn.com/images/53326505/original.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdata.whicdn.com%2Fimages%2F53326505%2Foriginal.jpg&h=1068cb73&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cfeaa8363bcc8d35f5fa15eba51e8925125fbb0b","tid":517154,"uid":8867,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T05:13:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3ddd962e18ebb33b1c29cbd2f38811ef16c7ce4a","tid":517154,"uid":55488,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T05:15:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c77e0e66c7c7a5c8c80369eb5917d992d3fdfbb1","tid":517154,"uid":100230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T05:28:20.000Z","msg":"入嚟就係為咗睇返啲圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a0707c698e31dae9cf751226c9312d372049ece","tid":517154,"uid":39174,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T06:13:45.000Z","msg":"係咪呀～輝<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f45e7eaef2b8efb4e6d2c72e0c029787b06a7ac","tid":517154,"uid":65587,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a770a628d9fc4bd39cf4e5f81f64c177c84cccb9","tid":517154,"uid":46769,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T04:54:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://data.whicdn.com/images/53326505/original.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdata.whicdn.com%2Fimages%2F53326505%2Forigina